    {
      "id": "PopularPost252095",
      "post_content": "Compare to [sanctum custodian](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=sanctum custodian). For one more {1}, you get a +1/+1 bonus. In terms of mana cost I probably would prefer the custodian, especially if I'm running [Mentor of the Meek](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mentor of the Meek), but I definitely dig this card, especially in a cleric tribal deck. Yet, [Master Apothecary](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Master Apothecary) makes most clerics with similar ability look like garbage. I'd definitely take this one though for the boost in toughness and theme redundancy, tossing one or, perhaps, two into the deck.  \n  \n[Mother of Ruins](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mother of Ruins), or if you have [Eight-and-a-Half-Tails](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eight-and-a-Half-Tails)  \n[Order of Whiteclay](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Order of Whiteclay)  \n[Daru Spiritualist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Daru Spiritualist), especially with [Shaman en-Kor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shaman en-Kor) and [Starlit Sanctum](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Starlit Sanctum) (props to @Silverware for this)  \n[Battletide Alchemist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Battletide Alchemist)  \n[Doubtless One](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doubtless One)  \n[Grand Abolisher](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grand Abolisher)  \n[Academy Rector](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Academy Rector)  \n[Preacher/autoca](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Preacher/autoca)... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "raptorman333",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost252095\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">Compare to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"sanctum custodian\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=sanctum custodian\">sanctum custodian</a>. For one more {1}, you get a +1/+1 bonus. In terms of mana cost I probably would prefer the custodian, especially if I'm running <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mentor of the Meek\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mentor of the Meek\">Mentor of the Meek</a>, but I definitely dig this card, especially in a cleric tribal deck. Yet, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Master Apothecary\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Master Apothecary\">Master Apothecary</a> makes most clerics with similar ability look like garbage.  I'd definitely take this one though for the boost in toughness and theme redundancy, tossing one or, perhaps, two into the deck.<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mother of Ruins\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mother of Ruins\">Mother of Ruins</a>, or if you have <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Eight-and-a-Half-Tails\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eight-and-a-Half-Tails\">Eight-and-a-Half-Tails</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Order of Whiteclay\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Order of Whiteclay\">Order of Whiteclay</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Daru Spiritualist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Daru Spiritualist\">Daru Spiritualist</a>, especially with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Shaman en-Kor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shaman en-Kor\">Shaman en-Kor</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Starlit Sanctum\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Starlit Sanctum\">Starlit Sanctum</a> (props to @Silverware  for this)<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Battletide Alchemist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Battletide Alchemist\">Battletide Alchemist</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Doubtless One\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doubtless One\">Doubtless One</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Grand Abolisher\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grand Abolisher\">Grand Abolisher</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Academy Rector\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Academy Rector\">Academy Rector</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Preacher/autoca\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Preacher/autoca\">Preacher/autoca</a>... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 252095)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '252095'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy17597\">raptorman333</span>\r\n                                (6/19/2012 10:04:58 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Right